{
  "stem": "7684.7",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when I came there, we-- we slept in these barracks, like you saw in pictures-- on the three row high.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I slept in the middle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one of the girls, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Ula ?] [INAUDIBLE]-- that also survived Sobibor-- she was born in Germany-- slept next to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you have always in camp a girl that-- that is your buddy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When you are very sick or something like that, that helps you and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she-- we were good-- friendly because we came-- know each other three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a barrel-- a pail inside that was the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a bathroom far away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just a hole where you went to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there-- and we got in the morning-- when we stand up, we didn't get any-- you know, it was so dirty there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just-- the people that slept there already, they tried to hold their self clean.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they looked clean because you could take the clothes-- you could steal clothes from the people that went to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So outside, you looked clean, but you was-- there was lice and-- and-- I don't know how you call these animals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In bed-- bed--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bed bugs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the blankets and everything was just-- it was-- we were very, very dirty because we couldn't wash our self the first month.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, two months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And later on, we got once a week a little pail with water that we can wash yourself a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
